headline: 2 Reasons to Like HUBB and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Since October 2020, the S&P 500 has delivered a total return of 97%. But one standout stock has more than doubled the market - over the past five years, Hubbell has surged 202% to $423.79 per share. Its momentum hasn’t stopped as it’s also gained 31.9% in the last six months thanks to its solid quarterly results, beating the S&P by 7.1%.
